  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 77321,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "@blackbibin reported password reset link not expiring when password was updated from an active session, by going to the Account's Login & Security setting. We were only expiring password reset links when the password was updated through a password reset request. Now we expire password reset links whenever a password is updated (besides regular time-based expiration). ",
